text.name: h2
text.content: This is one more Javascript game

text.name: p
text.content: As I say one more JS game. The game is a classical gambling game. Its a mix of bingo and lotto. This game does not exist, this is my imaginations.

text.name: p
text.content: When we click on play, we get a game panel. The game panel consists of header, body, and footer.

text.name: p
text.content: The game footer has a couple of components. First is a box to show how much we bet money. After that, we got a simple button for reset games. We can reset the game whenever we wanna.

text.name: p
text.content: The third component is a panel with a couple of functionality. The first one is above, this is a message place. Depending on the part of the game here we have different messages about games or instruction that we need to do. Under message is the total money we have, and next to we have an input field where we make bets.

text.name: p
text.content: Next is a small button for choosing another ticket, and the main button for start gameplay.

text.name: p
text.content: The game body consists of a couple of elements to. On the right side, we have a grid of 30 numbers. There we choosing a number for the ticket. Under that is selected numbers.  When we press the button 'DODAJ', we confirm the ticket. That ticket is showing on the left side. We have to confirm the 5 tickets. There we can see the number and quotes for tickets. In the middle, we have a list of rules for ticket win.

text.name: p
text.content: After the draw has finished, on the left we can see how many tickets we win. A green ticket is a winning ticket. Red Is a losing ticket.

text.name: p
text.content: Here we have an animated view of drawing numbers. Every ball is one number, and on every 2-sec new ball coming from a tube on the left side.

text.name: p
text.content: Before we start to roll for a ticket we have to make bets. Generally, we have to follow the message on board. There we have instruction for our next step. When we do this, we have to fill the ticket. We must have 5 tickets. Max's number per ticket is one and max five.

text.name: p
text.content: Every ticket has a quote. The quota depends on how many numbers we have on the ticket. If the ticket has one number value of him is 15. The quote for this ticket is 0.5. Calculation of winning money is 10 * bet money * quote. Ticket with 2 number has value 25 and quote 2. With three numbers 35 and quote 3. With 4 numbers value is 35 and quote 3. Next is 5 numbers with value 60 and quote, and the last one ticket value is 100 and quote 5. Inter alia this is bingo. We can hit multiple tickets at once.

text.name: p
text.content: When the draw is complete, we can roll again with the same tickets.

text.name: p
text.content: Or we can choose another one.

text.name: p
text.content: If we want we can reset the game to the start.
